SpreeSms
==========

Spree extension to send info/status SMS to a owner/developer using every SMS gateway service.

Installation
============

Add you Gemfile-file following line:
  gem 'spree_sms', :require => 'spree_sms', :git => 'git://github.com/sysadm/spree_sms.git'

Run: bundle install

Classic installation:
a) rake spree_sms:install
b) rake db:migrate

Pull requests welcome

